'''郗小星'''（英文：Xiaoxing Xi；{{bd|1957年}}）是一名美籍华裔物理学家。曾任[[費城|费城]][[天普大学|天普大学]]物理系系主任，[[劳拉·卡内尔|劳拉·卡内尔]]讲席教授<ref name="temple">{{cite web|title=Xiaoxing Xi|url=https://phys.cst.temple.edu/xiaoxing-xi.html|accessdate=2015-09-14|publisher=Temple University|archive-date=2015-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150927194822/https://phys.cst.temple.edu/xiaoxing-xi.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年5月，[[美国司法部|美国司法部]]将其逮捕，罪名是将受限制技术提供给中国，但在同年9月，针对他的所有指控均被撤销<ref name=":0">{{cite news|date=2015-10-21|title=The Two Asian Americas|newspaper=The New Yorker|url=http://www.newyorker.com/books/page-turner/the-two-asian-americas|accessdate=2020-11-03|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927082747/https://www.newyorker.com/books/page-turner/the-two-asian-americas|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=曾遭FBI指控涉經濟間諜等罪名 美籍華裔科學家郗小星獲頒人權獎|url=https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/389717/曾遭fbi指控涉經濟間諜等罪名-美籍華裔科學家郗小星獲頒人權獎|accessdate=2021-04-29|date=2019-10-23|last=米樂|work=香港01|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501023914/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/389717/%E6%9B%BE%E9%81%ADfbi%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%B6%89%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%96%93%E8%AB%9C%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA%E5%90%8D-%E7%BE%8E%E7%B1%8D%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%83%97%E5%B0%8F%E6%98%9F%E7%8D%B2%E9%A0%92%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E7%8D%8E|dead-url=no}}</ref>。郗小星因間諜指控背負巨額法律費用，提起的民事索償當局未予受理，遭遇的錯誤指控也未得到道歉和解釋。<ref>{{Cite web|title=美國華裔科學家被誤當間諜提民事索償遭拒 女兒斥政府帶頭歧視 ｜ 蘋果日報|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/7L2Z4O4SWBAVROVUJMMDZ63VLY/|accessdate=2021-04-29|work=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210504205019/https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210429/7L2Z4O4SWBAVROVUJMMDZ63VLY/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=The FBI wrongly accused my father of spying for China. Government has a role in anti-Asian violence.|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/opinion/voices/2021/04/27/chinese-american-professor-bias-fbi-attacks-government-column/7385996002/|accessdate=2021-04-29|last=Xi|first=Joyce|work=USA TODAY|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519111602/https://www.usatoday.com/story/opinion/voices/2021/04/27/chinese-american-professor-bias-fbi-attacks-government-column/7385996002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==职业==
郗小星生于中国，1987年获[[北京大学|北京大学]]博士学位。他曾是德国卡尔斯鲁厄核研究中心（{{lang|en|Karlsruhe Nuclear Research Center}}）的研究员，于1989年移居美国。他在美国[[罗格斯大学|罗格斯大学]]和[[马里兰大学|马里兰大学]]贝尔通讯研究部工作，1995年到[[宾夕法尼亚州立大学|宾夕法尼亚州立大学]]执教后入籍。<ref name=apuzzo>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/12/us/politics/us-drops-charges-that-professor-shared-technology-with-china.html |title=U.S. Drops Charges That Professor Shared Technology With China |date=2015-09-11 |author=Matt Apuzzo |newspaper=The New York Times |accessdate=2020-11-07 |archive-date=2020-10-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029011740/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/09/12/us/politics/us-drops-charges-that-professor-shared-technology-with-china.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=voa>{{cite news |url=http://www.voanews.com/content/feds-to-drop-fraud-charges-against-chinese-born-us-professor/2962631.html |title=Chinese-born Professor Faults US Authorities for Arrest |date=2015-09-14 |newspaper=Voice of America |accessdate=2020-11-03 |archive-date=2016-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105084211/http://www.voanews.com/content/feds-to-drop-fraud-charges-against-chinese-born-us-professor/2962631.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>郗小星的妻子曾在宾夕法尼亚州立大学任職物理学教授。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/voa-chinese-interview-xi-xiaoxing-temple-physicist/2962658.html |script-title=zh:美国之音中文部专访著名华裔学者郗小星 |date=2015-09-14 |newspaper=Voice of America |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190718121408/https://www.voachinese.com/a/voa-chinese-interview-xi-xiaoxing-temple-physicist/2962658.html |archivedate=2019-07-18 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2019-07-18 }}</ref>他们有两个女儿，住在费城郊区。<ref name="apuzzo" />2014年，郗小星任天普大学物理系主任。<ref name="temple" />

